{"tid":422980,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟有病既人係咪唔應該拍拖？","createTime":"2017-10-03T14:00:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-03T14:54:40.000Z","uid":57855,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c38fe83a9b43598df1e569c9d6abfe159ebeea3c","tid":422980,"uid":57855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T14:00:58.000Z","msg":"我係一個腦癇症患者 <br />\n一唔夠訓或者太攰就可能會暈低同抽搐<br />\n需要長期食藥先至唔會發作<br />\n女朋友知道我有呢個病但都無嫌棄我<br />\n但佢老母就係咁話會中風遺傳又唔知點咁<br />\n總之就極力反對我同我女朋友拍拖<br />\n開頭識落都好地地 一知道左我有病就變晒面<br />\n每次見到我同我女朋友Facetime 或者傾電話<br />\n就會係咁比d好難聽既說話我聽 每次我都好難受好想喊 點解我有病就要咁對我 明明我都無做錯到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dddc167397b70d3aa87ced4f7c46360999020ade","tid":422980,"uid":11484,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T14:01:59.000Z","msg":"我覺得如果兩個人都肯定左唔會生下一代<br />\n唔會怕遺傳個D其實冇野好煩<br />\n唔洗理佢老母"},{"pid":"3b1ff508593f8057b65de52891dcb36570a3fe8b","tid":422980,"uid":11893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T14:05:17.000Z","msg":"冇嫌棄你 你好好珍惜 唔洗理佢老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4da395620cb5ba7f6d9ad2fcb4e41924d272e4b","tid":422980,"uid":57855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T14:15:47.000Z","msg":"其他腦科醫生就話原因係未明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nThe seizures in epilepsy may be related to a brain injury or a family tendency, but often the cause is completely unknown."},{"pid":"15d85648a91a811e6c642d375decbc28d24b1c98","tid":422980,"uid":57855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T14:45:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfa997eada2afa6a676d5aa71db8c5ab670daa44","tid":422980,"uid":83597,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T14:54:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}